Coordinates: 503247N 42127W / 50.5463N 4.3575W / 50.5463; -4.3575 Bray Shop (Cornish: Shoppa Bre) is a village in east Cornwall, United Kingdom, in the civil parish of Linkinhorne. It is located on the B3257 approximately three miles north-northwest of Callington[1]. Media related to Bray Shop at Wikimedia Commons 
